cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.CYBER, cs.DS, cs.MM

The paper deals with spreading messages in social networks, which falls under the scope of social computing (cs.SOC) and social network analysis (cs.SI). The use of computerized bots to form spreading groups involves cybersecurity (cs.CYBER) and data science (cs.DS). The inspection of the model through a dataset of tweets suggests the involvement of multimedia (cs.MM) in the analysis.
